{
  "video_id": "4dn7TEjnbPY",
  "title": "Why should you read Tolstoy's \"War and Peace\"? - Brendan Pelsue",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7532.0,
      "end_time": 9393.0,
      "text": "&quot;War and Peace,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9393.0,
      "end_time": 10393.0,
      "text": "a tome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10393.0,
      "end_time": 11593.0,
      "text": "a slog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11593.0,
      "end_time": 14923.0,
      "text": "the sort of book you shouldn&#39;t read in bed because if you fall asleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14923.0,
      "end_time": 17953.0,
      "text": "it could give you a concussion, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17953.0,
      "end_time": 19492.0,
      "text": "Only partly."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19492.0,
      "end_time": 21703.0,
      "text": "&quot;War and Peace&quot; is a long book, sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21703.0,
      "end_time": 24734.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also a thrilling examination of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24734.0,
      "end_time": 30082.0,
      "text": "populated with some of the deepest, most realistic characters you&#39;ll find anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30082.0,
      "end_time": 35023.0,
      "text": "And if its length intimidates you, just image how poor Tolstoy felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35023.0,
      "end_time": 39412.0,
      "text": "In 1863, he set out to write a short novel about a political dissident"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39412.0,
      "end_time": 42213.0,
      "text": "returning from exile in Siberia."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42213.0,
      "end_time": 45807.0,
      "text": "Five years later, he had produced a 1,200 page epic"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45807.0,
      "end_time": 47064.0,
      "text": "featuring love stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47064.0,
      "end_time": 47995.0,
      "text": "battlefields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47995.0,
      "end_time": 48944.0,
      "text": "bankruptcies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48944.0,
      "end_time": 49933.0,
      "text": "firing squads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49933.0,
      "end_time": 51006.0,
      "text": "religious visions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51006.0,
      "end_time": 52332.0,
      "text": "the burning of Moscow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52332.0,
      "end_time": 54895.0,
      "text": "and a semi-domesticated bear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54895.0,
      "end_time": 57425.0,
      "text": "but no exile and no political dissidents."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57425.0,
      "end_time": 58995.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s how it happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 58995.0,
      "end_time": 60806.0,
      "text": "Tolstoy, a volcanic soul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60806.0,
      "end_time": 65624.0,
      "text": "was born to a famously eccentric  aristocratic family in 1828."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65624.0,
      "end_time": 69203.0,
      "text": "By the time he was 30, he had already dropped out of Kazan University,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69203.0,
      "end_time": 71184.0,
      "text": "gambled away the family fortune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71184.0,
      "end_time": 72254.0,
      "text": "joined the army,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 72254.0,
      "end_time": 73195.0,
      "text": "written memoirs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73195.0,
      "end_time": 77144.0,
      "text": "and rejected the literary establishment to travel Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 77144.0,
      "end_time": 80825.0,
      "text": "He then settled into Yasnaya Polyana, his ancestral mansion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80825.0,
      "end_time": 83734.0,
      "text": "to write about the return  of the Decembrists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83734.0,
      "end_time": 90554.0,
      "text": "a band of well-born revolutionaries pardoned in 1856 after 30 years in exile."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90554.0,
      "end_time": 91715.0,
      "text": "But, Tolstoy thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91715.0,
      "end_time": 94896.0,
      "text": "how could he tell the story  of the Decembrists return from exile"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94896.0,
      "end_time": 97485.0,
      "text": "without telling the story of 1825,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97485.0,
      "end_time": 101966.0,
      "text": "when they revolted against  the conservative Tsar Nicholas II?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101966.0,
      "end_time": 104876.0,
      "text": "And how could he do that without telling the story of 1812,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104876.0,
      "end_time": 107367.0,
      "text": "when Napoleon&#39;s disastrous  invasion of Russia"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107367.0,
      "end_time": 112245.0,
      "text": "helped trigger the authoritarianism the Decembrists were rebelling against?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112245.0,
      "end_time": 116239.0,
      "text": "And how could he tell the story of 1812 without talking about 1805,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116239.0,
      "end_time": 119086.0,
      "text": "when the Russians first learned of the threat Napoleon posed"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119086.0,
      "end_time": 123006.0,
      "text": "after their defeat at  the Battle of Austerlitz?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123006.0,
      "end_time": 124647.0,
      "text": "So Tolstoy began writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124647.0,
      "end_time": 126416.0,
      "text": "both about the big events of history"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126416.0,
      "end_time": 128917.0,
      "text": "and the small lives  that inhabit those events."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 128917.0,
      "end_time": 131867.0,
      "text": "He focused on aristocrats, the class he knew best."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131867.0,
      "end_time": 133506.0,
      "text": "The book only occasionally touches"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 133506.0,
      "end_time": 137167.0,
      "text": "on the lives of the vast majority  of the Russian population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137167.0,
      "end_time": 138797.0,
      "text": "who were peasants, or even serfs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138797.0,
      "end_time": 143287.0,
      "text": "farmers bound to serve the owners of the land on which they lived."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143287.0,
      "end_time": 147057.0,
      "text": "&quot;War and Peace&quot; opens on the eve of war between France and Russia."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147057.0,
      "end_time": 151001.0,
      "text": "Aristocrats at a cocktail party fret about the looming violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151001.0,
      "end_time": 154980.0,
      "text": "but then change the topic to those things aristocrats always seem to care about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154980.0,
      "end_time": 155761.0,
      "text": "money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155761.0,
      "end_time": 156512.0,
      "text": "sex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 156512.0,
      "end_time": 157752.0,
      "text": "and death."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 157752.0,
      "end_time": 159242.0,
      "text": "This first scene is indicative"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159242.0,
      "end_time": 162567.0,
      "text": "of the way the book bounces  between the political and personal"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162567.0,
      "end_time": 164809.0,
      "text": "over an ever-widening canvas."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 164809.0,
      "end_time": 167360.0,
      "text": "There are no main characters in &quot;War and Peace.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 167360.0,
      "end_time": 170438.0,
      "text": "Instead, readers enter a vast interlocking web"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 170438.0,
      "end_time": 172908.0,
      "text": "of relationships and questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 172908.0,
      "end_time": 175199.0,
      "text": "Will the hapless  and illegitimate son of a count"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175199.0,
      "end_time": 178268.0,
      "text": "marry a beautiful but conniving princess?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 178268.0,
      "end_time": 181409.0,
      "text": "Will his only friend survive the battlefields of Austria?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 181409.0,
      "end_time": 186618.0,
      "text": "And what about that nice young girl falling in love with both men at once?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186618.0,
      "end_time": 190519.0,
      "text": "Real historical figures mix and mingle with all these fictional folk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 190519.0,
      "end_time": 192616.0,
      "text": "Napoleon appears several times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 192616.0,
      "end_time": 197449.0,
      "text": "and even one of Tolstoy&#39;s ancestors plays a background part."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197449.0,
      "end_time": 200498.0,
      "text": "But while the characters  and their psychologies are gripping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 200498.0,
      "end_time": 202990.0,
      "text": "Tolstoy is not afraid to interrupt  the narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 202990.0,
      "end_time": 205990.0,
      "text": "to pose insightful  questions about history."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205990.0,
      "end_time": 207438.0,
      "text": "Why do wars start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 207438.0,
      "end_time": 209520.0,
      "text": "What are good battlefield tactics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209520.0,
      "end_time": 215189.0,
      "text": "Do nations rise and fall on the actions of so-called great men like Napoleon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215189.0,
      "end_time": 218829.0,
      "text": "or are there larger cultural and economic forces at play?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 218829.0,
      "end_time": 221940.0,
      "text": "These extended digressions are part  of what make &quot;War and Peace&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221940.0,
      "end_time": 223999.0,
      "text": "so panoramic in scope."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223999.0,
      "end_time": 225861.0,
      "text": "But for some 19th century critics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225861.0,
      "end_time": 230071.0,
      "text": "this meant &quot;War and Peace&quot; barely felt like a novel at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230071.0,
      "end_time": 234799.0,
      "text": "It was a &quot;large, loose, baggy monster,&quot; in the words of Henry James."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 234799.0,
      "end_time": 236891.0,
      "text": "Tolstoy, in fact, agreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236891.0,
      "end_time": 239862.0,
      "text": "To him, novels were  a western European form."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239862.0,
      "end_time": 245030.0,
      "text": "Russian writers had to write differently because Russian people lived differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 245030.0,
      "end_time": 247101.0,
      "text": "&quot;What is &#39;War and Peace&#39;?&quot; he asked."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247101.0,
      "end_time": 248281.0,
      "text": "&quot;It is not a novel."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248281.0,
      "end_time": 250152.0,
      "text": "Still less an epic poem."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 250152.0,
      "end_time": 252492.0,
      "text": "Still less a historical chronicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 252492.0,
      "end_time": 256651.0,
      "text": "&#39;War and Peace&#39; is what the author wanted and was able to express"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256651.0,
      "end_time": 259700.0,
      "text": "in the form in which it was expressed.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 259700.0,
      "end_time": 264121.0,
      "text": "It is, in other words, the sum total of Tolstoy&#39;s imaginative powers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264121.0,
      "end_time": 266231.0,
      "text": "and nothing less."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 266231.0,
      "end_time": 268257.0,
      "text": "By the time &quot;War and Peace&quot; ends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 268257.0,
      "end_time": 272080.0,
      "text": "Tolstoy has brought his characters to the year 1820,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 272080.0,
      "end_time": 277362.0,
      "text": "36 years before the events he originally hoped to write about."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 277362.0,
      "end_time": 279532.0,
      "text": "In trying to understand his own times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 279532.0,
      "end_time": 283982.0,
      "text": "he had become immersed in the years piled up behind him."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 283982.0,
      "end_time": 287742.0,
      "text": "The result is a grand interrogation into history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287742.0,
      "end_time": 288571.0,
      "text": "culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 288571.0,
      "end_time": 289671.0,
      "text": "philosophy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 289671.0,
      "end_time": 290862.0,
      "text": "psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 290862.0,
      "end_time": 300862.0,
      "text": "and the human response to war."
    }
  ]
}